Task-04: Personal Portfolio Website
This project is a personal portfolio website designed to showcase skills, projects, and accomplishments as a web developer.
Features
Visual Appeal: Features an attractive and visually appealing layout crafted to capture visitors' attention.
Home Page: Includes a captivating headline, a professional photo, and a summary of skills.
About Me Section: Provides a detailed background, education, and professional experience.
Live Demo
Check out the live website here: https://vennela-123634.github.io/Task-04-Portfolio-Website/
How to Run Locally
Clone this repository: git clone [https://github.com/vennela-123634/Task-04-Portfolio.git](https://github.com/vennela-123634/Task-04-Portfolio.git)
Open index.html in your web browser to view the application.
